\id 2TH consultant approved; ready for publication. Published with 2004 Aruamu NT. Revised by Aruamu translation team in 2019-2020, with input from many Aruamus. 
\h 2 Tesalonika 
\toc3 2TE 
\toc2 2 Tesalonika 
\toc1 Ak…®nafarir Namba 2, Pol Tesalonikan Nguibam…®n Itir Sios Baghava an Osiri 
\mt1 Ak…®nafarir Namba 2, // Pol Tesalonikan Nguibam…®n Itir Sios Baghava an Osiri 
\mt2 O 
\mt1 2 Tesalonika 
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip Gumazamizir Tesalonikan nguibar ekiam…®n itiba, me ti n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amua ghaze, bizir manamra Krais ua izamin dughiam…®n otivam. Marazi ghaze, Ekiam Izamin Dughiam otogha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Pol ko Sailas ko Timoti Tesalonikabar n…®ghn…®ziba ak…®rasa ak…®nafarir kam osiri. 
\ip Pol kamagh…®n m…®gei, dughiar kam t…®ghar otivam. Gumazamiziba faragh God…®n akaba batogh…®va ak…®rim God gasaragham. Eght…® arazir kuram otogh gavgavighv…®ra ikiam. Eght…® g…®n God…®n Araziba adoghodozir gumazir mam azenaram otogham, egh a Krais…®n apanim damuam. 
\ip Pol gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n tugh gavgavigh egh os…®mt…®ziba ater. Pol kamaghsua, me uarira uarir akurvaghs…® pamtem ingar, mati a uab…® a ko ingari darasi me ami mok…®n. Me ingangaribar amus…® am…®rvaghan mark…®. Egh me igharazi darazir akurvaghs…® am…®rvaghan mark…®. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Ekiam Izamin Dughiam  // g…®n otogham 
\mr (Sapta 1--2) 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Aposel 17:1; 1 Tesalonika 1:1\x*K…® Pol, ko Sailas ko Timoti, e Tesalonikan itir sios bagha ak…®nafarir kam osiri, me God en Afeziam ko Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n poroghav itir gumazamiziba. 
\p  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Rom 1:7\x*God en Afeziam ko Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n apangkuvim ia damight…®ma, ia navir am…®rizim ik…®. 
\s1 Tesalonikaba os…®mt…®ziba ko m…®zazibar dughiam…®n tuivigha gavgafi 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 1 Tesalonika 1:2-3; 2 Tesalonika 2:13\x*En adarasi, e zurara ian ziaba d…®pon…®va ia bagh God m…®nab…®va God ko m…®k…®mam. E fo, ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim bar mogh…®ra gavgafi, ez…® ia bar mogh…®ra vaghvagha bar uarigh ifonge, ez…® arazir kam ek…®va ghuav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n bar deraz…®, e ia bagha God m…®nabi.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 2 Korin 7:4; 7:14; 1 Tesalonika 2:19; Akar Mogomem 1:9\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e tintinibar God…®n siosbar ghuegha ian ziaba fe. E arazir kurar apaniba ia gamiba bar dar gun me m…®g…®ava, os…®mt…®ziba sara me m…®gei. Egha e kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod…®n gumazamiziba me uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n tugha gavgavigha, os…®mt…®ziba ko m…®zaziba ateri.‚Äù 
\s1 God arazir aghuim…®n e tuis…®si 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Filipai 1:28\x*Ez…® bizir ia bativir kaba, God kamagh…®n en aka, an arazir aghuim gamua egha en araziba tuis…®si. Ia kamagh…®n ifonge, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam otogham. Kamagh…®n, ia m…®zaziba isi. Eght…® God suam, ia dera egh ia inigh dughiar kam…®n aven mangam.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Rom 12:19; Akar Mogomem 18:6-7\x*God…®n arazir aghuim a kamagh…®n damuam, gumazamizir os…®mt…®ziba ia gar…®ziba, a ua men os…®mt…®ziba ikarvagham.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Matyu 25:31; 1 Tesalonika 3:13; 4:16\x*Egh ian os…®mt…®zir dat…®r…®gh…®n ia ateriba God da g…®vagh, avughsazim ia dan…®ng…®va uaghan e dan…®ngam. Dughiar kam…®n Ekiam Iesus uan ensel…®n bar gavgavim itiba ko God…®n Nguibam ategh azenara otogham, eght…® e avughsam. An avir bar gavgavir m…®zariaba sara izam.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Onger Akaba 79:6; Aisaia 66:15; Jeremaia 10:25; Rom 2:8; 1 Pita 4:17\x*Egh God g…®fozir puvat…®ziba ko en Ekiam Iesus…®n Akar Aghuim…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®ziba, Iesus ivezir kuram me ikarvagham.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Aisaia 2:10; 2:19-21; Filipai 3:19; 2 Pita 3:7\x*Kamagh…®n amir gumazamiziba ivezir kurar kam inigh; bar ikuvigh mamagh…®ra ikiam. Egh me Ekiam…®n saghon ik…®va, uaghan an gavgavim…®n angazangarir ekiam…®n saghon ikiam.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Onger Akaba 68:35; 89:7; Kolosi 3:4; 1 Tesalonika 3:13\x*Ez…® Dughiar God at…®zim, Ekiam ua iz…®t…®ma an gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itiba, me an ziam f…®va, ziar ekiam a dan…®ng a bagh bar akuegham. Ia God…®n akar e ian tong…®n kunizim, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia dughiar kam…®n uaghan me ko ikiam. 
\s1 Pol God ko m…®k…®mt…® a Tesalonikaba gavgavim me dan…®ngam 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Kolosi 1:9; 1 Tesalonika 1:2-3\x*Ez…® e bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®gha zurara ia bagha e uan God ko m…®gei, eght…® a ian akurvagham. E kamaghsua, a ia damut…® arazir aghuir a damuasa ian diaziba, ia dar amuam. E a ko m…®k…®mt…®ma, a gavgavim ia dan…®ngam. Eght…® ia, arazir aghuir ia damuasa ifongeziba bar, ia dar amuam. Eght…® God…®n gavgavim ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim damut…®, an ekeveght…® ia arazir aghuir av…®ribar amuam.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Aisaia 24:15; Malakai 1:11; 1 Pita 1:7; 4:14\x*Ez…® arazir kam…®n ia Ekiam Iesus…®n ziam f…®t…®ma a uaghan ian ziaba fam. En God ko Ekiam Krais Iesus ian apangkuvigh egh bizir kabar amut…® da guizbang…®n otivam. 
\c 2  
\s1 God…®n Araziba adoghodozir gumazim otogham 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Matyu 24:31; 1 Tesalonika 4:13-17\x*En adarasi, e bizitam ia m…®k…®masa, en Ekiam Krais Iesus a uamategh izam, eght…® e a ko uari akuvagham. E kamaghsua, ia bar derav…®ra akar kam baragh.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Matyu 24:4; Efesus 5:6; 1 Jon 4:1\x*Gumazir taba ti ia m…®g…®a ghaze, Ekiam Izamin Dughiam otogha g…®fa. Gumazir mam…®n n…®ghn…®zim ghaze, God…®n Duam ti uan akar kam a gan…®ngiz…® an an gun m…®gei. O gumazir mam God…®n akam akura akar kam…®n gun m…®gei. O gumazir mam ghaze, e osirizir ak…®nafarir mam, akar kam an iti. Ez…® ia akar kam managh a baraki, ia zuam…®ra d…®gavir kuram damigh…®va okam n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Jon 17:12; 1 Timoti 4:1; 1 Jon 2:18; 4:3; Akar Mogomem 13:11-14\x*Ia gumazitam…®n gant…® a uan akatam o arazir an amitam…®n ia gifaran mark…®. Ia oragh! Dughiar kam puram otoghan kogham. Puvat…®. Faragh…®v…®ra gumazir av…®rim God…®n akaba batogh…®va ak…®rim ragh God gasaragham. Eght…® God…®n Araziba adoghodozir gumazir mam azenara otogham, gumazir kam God hel…®n a gas…®ghas…®gham.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Esekiel 28:2; Daniel 7:25; 11:36; 1 Korin 8:5; Akar Mogomem 13:6\x*Bizir gumazamiziba ziaba feba ko dar bora ghaze men godba o men aseba, a dar apanim…®n ikiam. Egh a uab…®ra uan ziam f…®va egh a bizir kaba bar da d…®kab…®ragham. Egh a God…®n D…®penim…®n aven daperagh ik…®va kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄúK…® uab…®ra God.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ia fo, k…® ia ko itir dughiam, k…® bizir kabar gun ia m…®keme. Ia ti ok…®n…®ghn…®ghiz, o?  
\v 6 Ia fo, bizir mam gumazir kam…®n tuavim ap…®rima an azenaram otivan kogham. A g…®n God a bagha at…®zir dughiamra, an azenim giram.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt 1 Jon 2:18; 4:3\x*Ia fo, dat…®r…®gh…®n God…®n Araziba adoghodozir arazir kam averara ingari iti. A modogh averara ik…® mang…®t…®, gumazir an tuavim ap…®rizim, s…®vagh mang…®t…®, an azenaram otogham.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Jop 4:9; Aisaia 11:4; Daniel 7:10; Hibru 10:27; Akar Mogomem 19:15\x*Egh God…®n Araziba adoghodozir gumazir kam dughiar kam…®n azenim giram. Eght…® Ekiam Iesus uan akam…®n a giveragh a m…®sueght…®ma an aremegham. Ekiam uan angazangarim ko gavgavir ekiam sara iz…®va, uan angazangarim ko gavgavir kamra a gumazir kam bar a gas…®ghas…®gham.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Matyu 24:24; Jon 8:41; Efesus 2:2; Akar Mogomem 13:11-13; 18:23; 19:20\x*God…®n Araziba adoghodozir gumazir kam, a Satan…®n gavgavim…®n azenan otogham. Egh Satan…®n ifavarir arazim…®n, a d…®gavir kuram gamir arazir av…®riba ko arazarazir igharaziba ko mirakel…®n ifavarir igharagha gariba, dar amuam.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt 2 Korin 2:15; 4:3\x*An arazir kurar av…®rir igharazibar amu, ovevem…®n tuavim…®n g…®n zuir gumazibagh ifaram. Me guiz…®n akam gifongeghan aghua, ez…® God men akuraghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamizir kaba bar ar…®ghiregham.  
\v 11-12 \x - \xo 2:11-12 \xt Matyu 24:5; 24:11; Rom 1:24; 1:32; 1 Timoti 4:1; 2 Timoti 4:4\x*God kamaghsua, gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim guiz…®n akam…®n itir puvat…®gha arazir kurabagh amua bar akongeziba, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim akar ifavarim…®n ik…®va, God…®n kot…®n ivezir kuram iniam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God men n…®ghn…®zibagh amiz…®, me paza n…®ghn…®si. 
\s1 God ua ia iniasa ia m…®sefe 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Luk 1:75; Jon 15:16; Efesus 1:4; 1 Tesalonika 4:7; 5:9; 2 Tesalonika 1:3\x*En darasi, ia Ekiam bar ifongeziba, God faragha inizir gumazamizibar tong…®n ikiasa ia m…®sefe. God uan Duam…®n gavgavim…®n ian navir averiam…®n ingarima, ia a baghav…®ra itir gumazamiziba, egha ia guiz…®n akam n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti. Ez…® tuavir kam…®n God ian akurvaghasa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e zurara God ia bagh a m…®namam.  
\v 14 God kamaghsua, ia uan Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n angazangarir ekiam…®n aven a ko ikiasa a ifonge. Egha a uan Akar Aghuir e ia m…®kemezir kam…®n ian dia.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Korin 11:2; 16:13; Filipai 4:1; 2 Tesalonika 3:6\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, en adarasi, ia bar tuivigh gavgafigh. Eght…® God…®n akar e ia m…®kemeziba, o akar ian sure damuasa osiriziba, ia dar g…®n mang…®. 
\p  
\v 16 E kamagh…®n God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, en Ekiam Krais Iesus ko God en Afeziam bar e gifonge. Egha en apangkuvigha en navibagh amima, da deragh, mamagh…®ra ikiam. Egha en akurvazima en n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikiava God m…®zuai, eght…® an arazir aghuim…®n e damuam.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt 1 Korin 1:8; 1 Tesalonika 3:13; 1 Pita 5:10\x*Egh a gavgavim ian navibar an…®ng, ian akurvaght…® ia arazir aghuiba bar, dar g…®n mang…®va akar aghuibav k…®mam. 
\c 3  
\ms1 Tesalonikaba gumazamizir ingangaribar am…®razibar  // arazibar k…®righ 
\mr (Sapta 3) 
\s1 Ia God ko m…®k…®mt…®, an en akuragham 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Efesus 6:19; Kolosi 4:3; 1 Tesalonika 5:25\x*En adarasi, en akar abuananam, a kamak…®n. Ia God ko m…®k…®mt…®ma, an en akuragham, eght…® Ekiam…®n akam zuam…®ra nguibaba bar a dar mang…®t…® gumazamiziba a iniva an g…®n mang…®, n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikiam, mati ia faragha a iniz…® mok…®n.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Aposel 28:24; Rom 10:16; 15:31\x*Ia God ko m…®k…®mt…®ma a gumazir kurabar dafaribar e inigh, kar arazir kurabagh amir gumaziba. Ia fo, gumazamizir maba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ekiam…®n itir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Jon 17:15; 1 Korin 1:9; 1 Tesalonika 5:24; 2 Pita 2:9\x*Ez…® Ekiam guiz…®n arazibagh ami, eght…® ia bar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavimra an ik…®. A gavgavim ia dan…®ng…®va, ia geghuvt…®, Satan paza ia damighan kogham.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt 2 Korin 7:16; Galesia 5:10; 1 Tesalonika 4:10\x*Ez…® Ekiam e gamiz…®ma e bar derav…®ra kamagh…®n fo, ia arazir e ia m…®kemeziba, bar dagh amuav…®ra iti. Egh g…®n ia kamagh…®ra damuam. 
\p  
\v 5 E kamaghsua, Ekiam ian faragh mang…®, ian navibar amut…®, ia fogh suam, God guizbang…®ra ia gifonge. A ian navibar amut…®, ia Krais…®n arazim…®n g…®n mang…®va os…®mt…®ziba ater…®va tugh gavgavigham. 
\s1 Gumazamiziba bar, ingangaribar amu 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Matyu 18:17; Rom 16:17; 1 Korin 5:11-13; 2 Tesalonika 3:11-14; 1 Timoti 6:5; 2 Jon 1:10\x*En adarasi, en Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n ziam…®n e akar gavgavim m…®g…®a kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, en marazi pura am…®rvagha ikia, akar e ia gan…®ngizim…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®. Ia vaghvagh men saghon ik…®.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt 1 Korin 4:16; Filipai 3:17; 1 Tesalonika 1:6\x*Ia fo, ia en arazibar g…®n mang…®. Dughiar e ia ko itiba, e pura apiaghav itir puvat…®.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt 2 Korin 11:9; 1 Tesalonika 2:9\x*E pura ian dafaribar daghetaba inizir puvat…®. E dagh ivesi. E kamaghsua, e os…®mt…®ziba ia dar…®ghan kogham. Kamagh…®n e puv…®ra arueba ko d…®magaribar ingari.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt 1 Korin 9:4-6; 1 Tesalonika 1:6\x*God ghaze, e dagheba bagh ian azangs…®ght…®ma, ia en akurvagham. Ez…® e ian azangs…®zir pu. E ghaze, e arazir aghuim ian akaght…®ma ia an g…®n mangam. Ez…® kamagh…®n, e ian azangs…®zir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt 1 Tesalonika 4:11\x*Ia fo, dughiar e ia ko itibar, e akar gavgavim ia gan…®ngi: gumazamiziba ingangaribar amuan aghuaght…®, ia dagheba me dan…®ngan kogham. 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt 1 Timoti 5:13; 1 Pita 4:15\x*Ez…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n orazi, ian marazi pura iti. Me ingangaritam gamir puvat…®. Me pura gumazamizir igharazibar biziba tintinibar dav gei. Kar men biziba puvat…®.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt 1 Tesalonika 4:11\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n ziam…®n e akar gavgavir kam kamagh…®n gumazir kabav gei, me bar derav…®ra dapiagh…®va, ingar…®va, me daghebar uarira uarir akurvagh. 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Galesia 6:9\x*Ez…® en adarasi, ia arazir aghuibar amuva dar am…®rvaghan mark…®. 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt 1 Korin 5:9-11\x*Eght…® gumazitam o amizitam akar e ak…®nafarir kam…®n osirizibar g…®n mangan koght…®ma, ia derav…®ram an gan. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, gumazir kam uan arazir kam g…®fogh…®va aghums…®gham, kamagh…®n ia an saghon ik…®.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt 1 Tesalonika 5:14; Taitus 3:10\x*Ia apanim…®n m…®n a g…®n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, ia aveghbuam…®n m…®n a damuva, egh arazir aghuibar amus…® an sure damu. 
\s1 Pol uan akar abuananam me gan…®di 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt 1 Tesalonika 5:23\x*Ekiam a navir am…®rizim…®n m…®ngarim, a zurara ia damut…® ia navir am…®rizim…®n biziba bar dar ikiam. Ekiam bar mogh…®ra ia ko ikiam. 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt 1 Korin 16:21\x*K…® Pol, k…® uan dafarim…®n osira ghaze, Afeziam ia ko ik…®. Nan ak…®nafariba bar, osizirir abuananam k…® zurara uan ziam kamagh…®n an osiri. Kar k…® kamagh…®n osiri. 
\p  
\v 18 En Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n apangkuvim bar mogh…®ra ia ko ikiam.